lucida/kaldi-gst-asr for Debian
----------------

Source include both Kaldi, kaldi-gtreamer-ast, and some more
Binary include Kaldi and kaldi-gtreamer-ast

--- Build and install ---
build with:
   dpkg-buildpackage
(missing required packages will be shown)
(advanced users may prefer debuild or sbuild)

install the .deb package via GUI or with:
   dpkg -i lucida*.deb
   apt-get install -f
 
